window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Costillian Empire sent Levi and his lovers reeling, yet they weren't defeated. Regrouping, they are setting out to find some of the most powerful beings on Taryl in the hopes of turning the tide. Their adventure will lead them to leave Taryl and explore a new dimension... and when they return, the empire will discover why Demon Lords have been feared for so long.</p> <p>Enjoy book 5 in the ongoing saga of Levi Walker, Demon Lord of the Otherworld Academy. This book contains unusual relationships, sassy beast companions, and interdimensional beings with strange moralities.</p>"; 
